race.comment: CRITICAL MOMENT (2) lines up chasing another win after sizzling around Bulli over 400m in 22.33 on September 30. Smart win latest and looks a key chance again here. LOGISTICAL (6) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when eighth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Fancy Bella (31.29) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Has a strong record from box 6, including two wins. Key runner on best form. ZIPPY ZENDEN (8) is progressing well with another good run, placing by 4.5 lengths (25.60) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can feature again. IRINKA ALANA (1) scored in dominant fashion last time. Hard to beat again.
